and ask for the right to speak

483
00:34:01,206 --> 00:34:02,832
before taking the floor.

484
00:34:02,916 --> 00:34:05,293
I request your cooperation
during this meeting.

485
00:34:05,377 --> 00:34:06,878
Sir.

486
00:34:06,962 --> 00:34:10,423
