487
00:34:10,507 --> 00:34:13,301
-Ridiculous? How could you say that?
-Wait!

488
00:34:13,385 --> 00:34:14,761
-Once again…
-That's enough!

489
00:34:14,844 --> 00:34:16,513
-I'd like to…
-Good grief.

490
00:34:16,596 --> 00:34:18,098
ask all of you

491
00:34:18,765 --> 00:34:21,059
to cooperate with me here.

492
00:34:21,142 --> 00:34:23,979
Keep your mouth shut, Lee Soo-min!

493
00:34:24,604 --> 00:34:26,565
Show some respect!

494
00:34:27,857 --> 00:34:29,401
Assemblyman Kang.

495
00:34:29,985 --> 00:34:31,361
You owe her an apology.

496
00:34:32,362 --> 00:34:33,321
I apologize.

497
00:34:34,114 --> 00:34:35,198
Unbelievable.

498
00:34:35,699 --> 00:34:36,866
Sir.

499
00:34:36,950 --> 00:34:38,451
We are against this.

500
00:34:40,412 --> 00:34:41,830
Assemblyman Kang.

501
00:34:42,831 --> 00:34:45,417
If you have questions about the bill,

502
00:34:45,500 --> 00:34:47,419
discuss it with us and ask questions.

503
00:34:48,003 --> 00:34:51,131
Stop picking a fight
with the Daehan Party.

504
00:34:52,757 --> 00:34:54,092
"Picking a fight"?

505
00:34:54,843 --> 00:34:55,677
Goodness.

506
00:34:56,303 --> 00:34:58,221
You failed to convince us.

507
00:34:58,805 --> 00:35:01,057
You should admit to your faults.

508
00:35:01,141 --> 00:35:02,475
Good grief.

509
00:35:02,559 --> 00:35:04,728
How could you accuse me
of picking a fight?

510
00:35:05,312 --> 00:35:06,730
My goodness.

511
00:35:06,813 --> 00:35:10,609
-It would be easier to talk to my dog.
-I agree.

512
00:35:10,692 --> 00:35:12,819
Did you just compare me to a dog?

513
00:35:22,746 --> 00:35:24,331
Dear Assemblyman Kang.

514
00:35:25,290 --> 00:35:26,833
This is the National Assembly.

515
00:35:27,709 --> 00:35:30,670
The language you use
when you're drinking at a bar

516
00:35:30,754 --> 00:35:33,089
has no place here
in the National Assembly.

517
00:35:34,758 --> 00:35:38,094
You should know better.

518
00:35:44,225 --> 00:35:45,727
Please apologize for your remark.

519
00:35:54,819 --> 00:35:56,237
I apologize.

520
00:36:05,372 --> 00:36:07,123
How may I help you?

521
00:36:08,416 --> 00:36:09,959
