522
00:36:10,710 --> 00:36:11,878
Sure.

523
00:36:17,133 --> 00:36:18,968
<i><font color="white">Would you like the receipt?</font></i>

524
00:36:20,178 --> 00:36:21,346
BALANCE: 1.3 MILLION WON

525
00:36:21,429 --> 00:36:22,555
